+   [2]: https://golang.org/ "Go Language"
+   [3]: https://github.com/vmg/sundown "Sundown"
+   [4]: https://godoc.org/gopkg.in/russross/blackfriday.v2#Parse "Parse func"
+   [5]: https://github.com/microcosm-cc/bluemonday "Bluemonday"
